oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mildred McIntosh
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of Miss Mildred M. McIntosh, of Elbridge, Tenn., Queen of Juvenile Dairy Show, standing next to the 3 year old Grand Champion Jersey cow, "Dreaming Sybil Mille." She is smiling and wearing a watch. The cow has on a metallic crown.
Owner of the cow: Louis Robinson, Pulaski, Tenn.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
